\pard\tx1440\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\qj\fi0\sb80\sa0\li0\ri0\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\scaps0\cf0 Here there are four main groups.  The first and last group are instrumental, and so the bar lines have been set to show through the staves.  The middle two groups are vocal: the first group has an extra bracket to group the sopranos, and the second group has a n extra bracket to group the tenors.  The system has been set to have an additional 3\i ss\i0  of leading between the main groups.\par
